prompt_text_japanese ONLY. The English prompt_text contains the
speaking challenge only.
 
 
CROSS-COMPETENCY VOCABULARY NOTE
----------------------------------
C2 introduces vocabulary that recycles and extends C1 vocabulary:
- C1 taught: "How about you?" (ask back)
- C2 extends: "What happened?" / "How did it go?" (specific follow-ups)
This connection should be made explicit in Week 11 Day 2 Grammar Tip
for all purposes — a brief note acknowledging "You already know how to
ask back. Now let's make those questions more specific."
 
 
